##Inputs added vs E-commerce Engine
1. Platform checkboxes (Tiktok, Instagram, Youtube)
2. Video format selector (clip/storyboard/both)
The storyboard option provides:
- Hook (0-2s) aimed to grab scroller's attention
- Scene (2-8s) the main visual action
- Scene 2 (8-15s) the product highlight or key message
- Close/CTA (last 2s) how it ends
- Audio direction (music, tempo, energy)
- Video type (UGC, lifestyle, talking head)
3. Brand social content folder (examples of their social media presence)

---
##Outputs
1. Seperate image and video prompts per product.
2. Allowed to download prompts as a zip file.
